Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:18.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:32.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I covered my ears with my hands, and my\Nforehead swelled up and grew four horns.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:42.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If on a snowy night, you can hear no sound,\Ntalk to someone, or close your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:47.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or your ears will be consumed.
