Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:03:00.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:05.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the Mushi-shi... Ginko-san, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:06.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:09.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Shirasawa, the village chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:12.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I called you here on behalf of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:17.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,As you can see, we live in the depths\Nof a vast mountain range.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:21.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's very quiet here; the wind does not pass through.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:27.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,In particular on a snowy night like\Nthis, it becomes dead silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:31.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's said that even voices often vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:36.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when that happens, some people lose their hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:39.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,In both of their ears?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:42.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just one for most.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:47.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The doctors in town just shake their heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:52.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I suspected that it may be something paranormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:05.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, this mucus...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:09.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mushi is the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:12.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's called an Un.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:16.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's consuming all the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:23.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Normally they live in the forests, but\Nthe snow is absorbing all the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:27.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So they must have come to this\Nvillage in search of sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:36.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, there they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:40.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a big swarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:43.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'd be the ones eating all the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:53.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So they leave their swarms and infect animal hosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:55.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like a snail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:01.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:02.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:07.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you know that there's an organ in\Nour ears that looks just like a snail?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:16.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A starved Un will leave its shell, infest in\Nthat organ, and consume all sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:20.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, the organ isn't destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:21.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:25.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this enough hot water?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:26.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:34.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pour this in your ear, and it should...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:50.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hot, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:54.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:56.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Salt?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:58.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:05.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just spread the rest of that around the attic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:09.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:13.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never seen a Mushi-shi at work before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:17.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just one more left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:20.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's one more, who has lost hearing in both ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:24.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:30.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,His symptons aren't like the others'.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:37.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please don't tell the others how my grandson is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:57.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:00.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:10.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Maho.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:13.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It began last winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:17.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,These horns grew on his head,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:23.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and he lost all ability to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:28.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Instead he hears sounds that he's never heard before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:35.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even on a silent night like this,\Nhe hears sounds from all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:39.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whispering sounds, thundering sounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:42.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'd close his ears really tight, but it's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:45.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sound's coming in from his horns, he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:51.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could this be... an Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:52.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:58.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They live alongside the Un. They consume\Nthe silence created by the Un.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:04.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once you're infected with one, you'll\Nstart picking up any sound you can,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:07.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the sounds from your\Nsurroundings are drowned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:12.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they are a very rare Mushi compared to the Un.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:16.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's only one recorded attempt at treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:25.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to that, applying salt water to the ears\Ndidn't have the same effect as on an Un.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:31.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Many other medicines were tried,\Nbut none were successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:36.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the end of the winter following the infection,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:43.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,the patient broke down from the endless torrents\Nof sound rushing in day and night,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:47.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and eventually died of weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:52.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The winter following...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:09:00.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, we need to know our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:17.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:24.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the noise is a bit quieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:29.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It got really loud since you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:32.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My head was about to explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:34.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:38.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I seem to be the type to attract Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:40.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're loud things, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:43.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I drove them off with this smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:44.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:47.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:49.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most of it, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:53.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Humans have an exceptionally bad sense of hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:58.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Other animals can distinguish\Na much wider range of sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:04.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's said that there's a range of sounds\Nthat not even animals can hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:07.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the range of the Mushi's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:12.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are the Mushi talking this loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:16.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Each Mushi has a tiny voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:21.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there are countless Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:25.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If all those Mushi speak one thing, what happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:31.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's said that their voice bellows across the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:39.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Ah in your ears are consuming your silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:44.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then those horns of yours grow, and you\Nbegin to hear all sorts of sounds from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:47.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That seems to be what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:51.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your ears look perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:55.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did those horns grow?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:02.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had my hands over my ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:09.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My mom died last winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:17.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remembered that Mom would do it all\Nthe time, so I tried doing the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:24.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then my forehead bulged up, and the horns grew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:28.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She held her ears?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:31.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did she do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:33.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:35.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:41.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom had the same sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:45.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Holding her ears couldn't have helped at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:50.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom said something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:59.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and held my ears tight with her weakened hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:04.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when I try to recall what she said...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:07.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know I remember what she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:10.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I keep trying to recall it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.91,0:12:16.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the noise keeps rushing into\Nmy head, and I can't hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:19.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:25.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're... rather unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:28.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To have an example of the exact same symptoms,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:32.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}means that there must be a key to a treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:42.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My daughter's death?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:46.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was very miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:50.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She could hardly sleep, because of the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:54.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She never said this in Maho's presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:59.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But she'd often say,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:05.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to sleep quietly; somewhere where\Nabsolutely no sound can reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:11.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like you explained earlier,\Nthe winter after the attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:14.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,she left for the place which she wished to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:19.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So she was distressed by the noise until the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:20.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:22.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:25.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:28.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:33.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mom, the noise is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:36.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's dead silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:38.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:40.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:45.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I long for that sound that I dreaded so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:55.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And shortly after, she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:14:00.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So right before her death, she lost all hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:01.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:03.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:10.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, but this must be what Maho\Nwas talking about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:14.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it was strange myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:17.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did my child do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:22.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The silence before death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:27.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did the Ah anticipate its host's death and flee?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:32.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, then she should have regained hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:36.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What does it mean to hear nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:41.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And what did she want to shut her ears from?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:47.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where you headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:49.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, you can't hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:52.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:54.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:14:58.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just going for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:00.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:07.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go crazy if I stay inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:10.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:18.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I keep remembering about the time Mom died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:26.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fair enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:31.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He saw his mother pass away with the same illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:40.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's snowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:43.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shouldn't have let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:44.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maho,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:45.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maho.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:49.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Ginko-san, I can't find Maho.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:50.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:52.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know which way he went.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:53.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:55.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You let him go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:57.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:03.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:10.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's not perfectly silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:16.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen carefully and you can even\Nhear the snow accumulate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:21.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And when it's quiet around you, you\Ncan hear your own heart beating.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:30.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the sounds lose their destinction\Nwhen there is too much around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:37.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And in the extreme –
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:45.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could that be the same as sound disappearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:47.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:02.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:05.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was going to go home right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:09.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got caught in the snowstorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:13.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I was waiting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:17.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's getting stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:20.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? His voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:39.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:42.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,quit fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:45.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which one of you is the Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:50.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uns are right-winding, Ahs are left-winding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:51.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:12.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maho, can you lend me your hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:15.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The way your mother did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:27.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:40.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It melted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:46.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You won't get pure silence by holding your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:52.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not that your mother wanted to\Nshut her ears out from anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:56.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wanted to hear what she could\Nhear with her hands over her ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:18:59.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:06.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hear a tiny rumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:10.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the sound of the muscles in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:16.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, Ah's weakness must be\Nthe sound of another being's vitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:21.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that sound is always there\Nrumbling inside of the living.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:25.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sound must not be comfortable to the Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:29.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it tries to quell the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:33.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whether the Ah melts or the host dies,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:40.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,is determined in approximately a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:43.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your daughter must have come to realize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:48.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But by then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:51.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,she was already too weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:53.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maho,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:56.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,can you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:19:59.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is your mother's sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:10.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw a mountain erupt, a long time ago with your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:18.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This sound is just like the sound of the lava.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:26.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So when I'm so worried that I could\Njust vanish, I listen to this sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:30.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It melts away all my fear and pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:38.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,the way lava melts everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:42.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, you try it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:46.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a stream of lava within you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:00.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maho?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:03.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lava...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:05.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maho.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.83,0:21:12.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's bright red lava flowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:21.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take this as my pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:22.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:25.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that really all you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:26.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:28.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that good, Maho?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:49.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The world's quiet, isn't it, Maho?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:55.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll take a while to get used to it, and you'll\Ncrave for the world you just parted with.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:22:03.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you'll forget by the time spring comes\Nand it gets lively around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.26,0:22:07.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.76,0:22:14.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was always listening to the same sound Mom was.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.60,0:22:21.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sound so beautiful that it gives me chills.
